metadata.name: Nr_15
metadata.description:
Is this the balance we have been working towards?
-
Avril has landed in a time and space where Mother Nature and technology have intermingled. By the efforts of countless bright minds there now exists an equilibrium of the metaverse and the ecosphere. Cybernetic enhancements are working together with compounds found in the wild to take the human mind to places where it hasn't been before. Flora and fauna have the possibility to thrive without the destructive impact of human greed. The planet is not only surviving, but it is thriving. The course has been corrected and the future seems brighter than ever. 
-
The possibilities are endless here.
